44#include "aslcompiler.h"
45
46#define _COMPONENT ACPI_COMPILER
47 ACPI_MODULE_NAME ("asluuid")
48
49
50extern UINT8 AcpiGbl_MapToUuidOffset[UUID_BUFFER_LENGTH];
51
52
53/*******************************************************************************
54 *
55 * FUNCTION: AuValiduateUuid
56 *
57 * PARAMETERS: InString - 36-byte formatted UUID string
58 *
59 * RETURN: Status
60 *
61 * DESCRIPTION: Check all 36 characters for correct format
62 *
63 ******************************************************************************/
64
65ACPI_STATUS
66AuValidateUuid (
67 char *InString)
68{
69 UINT32 i;
70
71
72 if (!InString || (strlen (InString) != UUID_STRING_LENGTH))
73 {
74 return (AE_BAD_PARAMETER);
75 }
76
77 /* Check all 36 characters for correct format */
78
79 for (i = 0; i < UUID_STRING_LENGTH; i++)
80 {
81 /* Must have 4 hyphens (dashes) in these positions: */
82
83 if ((i == UUID_HYPHEN1_OFFSET) ||
84 (i == UUID_HYPHEN2_OFFSET) ||
85 (i == UUID_HYPHEN3_OFFSET) ||
86 (i == UUID_HYPHEN4_OFFSET))
87 {
88 if (InString[i] != '-')
89 {
90 return (AE_BAD_PARAMETER);
91 }
92 }
93 else
94 {
95 /* All other positions must contain hex digits */
96
97 if (!isxdigit ((int) InString[i]))
98 {
99 return (AE_BAD_PARAMETER);
100 }
101 }
102 }
103
104 return (AE_OK);
105}
106
107
108/*******************************************************************************
109 *
110 * FUNCTION: AuConvertUuidToString
111 *
112 * PARAMETERS: UuidBuffer - 16-byte UUID buffer
113 * OutString - 36-byte formatted UUID string
114 *
115 * RETURN: Status
116 *
117 * DESCRIPTION: Convert 16-byte UUID buffer to 36-byte formatted UUID string
118 * OutString must be 37 bytes to include null terminator.
119 *
120 ******************************************************************************/
121
122ACPI_STATUS
123AuConvertUuidToString (
124 char *UuidBuffer,
125 char *OutString)
126{
127 UINT32 i;
128
129
130 if (!UuidBuffer || !OutString)
131 {
132 return (AE_BAD_PARAMETER);
133 }
134
135 for (i = 0; i < UUID_BUFFER_LENGTH; i++)
136 {
137 OutString[AcpiGbl_MapToUuidOffset[i]] =
138 AcpiUtHexToAsciiChar (UuidBuffer[i], 4);
139
140 OutString[AcpiGbl_MapToUuidOffset[i] + 1] =
141 AcpiUtHexToAsciiChar (UuidBuffer[i], 0);
142 }
143
144 /* Insert required hyphens (dashes) */
145
146 OutString[UUID_HYPHEN1_OFFSET] =
147 OutString[UUID_HYPHEN2_OFFSET] =
148 OutString[UUID_HYPHEN3_OFFSET] =
149 OutString[UUID_HYPHEN4_OFFSET] = '-';
150
151 OutString[UUID_STRING_LENGTH] = 0; /* Null terminate */
152 return (AE_OK);
153}
